properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 17 at 8:42AM PST until January 19 at 4:00AM PST by NWS Seattle WA
properties.description:
* WHAT...Combined seas 6 to 7 ft building to 10 to 13 ft Saturday
morning. Bar conditions moderate, becoming rough Saturday
morning.

* WHERE...Grays Harbor Bar.

* WHEN...From 4 AM Saturday to 4 AM PST Sunday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft especially
when navigating in or near harbor entrances.
properties.instruction:
A Small Craft Advisory for rough bar means that wave conditions
are expected to be hazardous to small craft in or near harbor
entrances.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 4 AM SATURDAY TO 4 AM PST SUNDAY
